'''Marcos Andr<U+00E9> Rocha Costa''' (born [[April 6]], [[1979]] in [[Salvador, Bahia]]) is a [[Boxing|boxer]] from [[Brazil]], who won the bronze medal in the [[light welterweight]] division (&ndash; 64 kg) at the [[Boxing at the 2003 Pan American Games|2003 Pan American Games]] in [[Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic]].

